com.dlsc.flexgantt.model.scheduling

Interface IModelValidator

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    DefaultModelValidator

    public interface IModelValidator
    A model validator is used to verify whether any relationships or constraints inside a given Gantt chart model have been violated. The result of the validation is a list of messages that can be added to the Gantt chart.
    Since:
    2.1
    Author:
    Dirk Lemmermann
